snippet.title: Anno 1800 New World Rising CGI Teaser for DLC 12 | Ubisoft Forward
snippet.description:
Discover a sneak peak of the "New World Rising" DLC of Anno 1800 with this CGI teaser. This DLC will feature a new population level never seen before in the New World and will be available this winter. 

#anno1800 #ubisoftforward #gaming
